{"lastModified":1774958644627,"uri":"c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Based in Mykonos, this beautiful Ferretti 630 offers a comfortable and relaxing way to explore the Greek islands. \nThe yacht completed a refit in 2026, with several upgrades that improve both comfort and the overall experience on board.\n\nThe salon is bright and welcoming, featuring electric shades and a sound isolation system, allowing guests to enjoy different music or entertainment in separate areas if they wish. The interior has also been refreshed with new flooring, new mattresses in the cabins, and updated amenities, linens, and towels for extra comfort.\nGuests can also enjoy a variety of water toys, perfect for spending fun moments in the sea.\nOn board, guests are looked after by an experienced captain who ensures a safe and enjoyable trip.\n\nThe Ferretti 630 is ideal for guests looking for a comfortable and relaxed day or multi-day experience on the water.","blueprint":{"name":"ESCAPE","images":["/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::537eb140-17b4-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::537dc6e0-17b4-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::537eff60-17b4-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::537f7490-17b4-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::537f4d80-17b4-11f1-a477-8d9991fc3e28/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::c8846d80-3c69-11f0-a3e5-b16aafb5da62/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::c86f37