label":"Washing Machine"},{"label":"Heating System"},{"label":"Outside Shower"},{"label":"Sun Pads"},{"label":"GPS Plotter"},{"label":"Solar Panels"},{"label":"Teak deck (whole deck, not only the cockpit)"},{"label":"Electric winches"},{"label":"Radar"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Autopilot"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Bow thruster"},{"label":"Bathing platform"},{"label":"Generator"}],"toys":[{"label":"Jetski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"E-foil","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Seabob","quantity":"4"},{"label":"SUP","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Water ski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Wake board","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Tubes","quantity":"1"}],"entertainment":["Outside deck speakers","Radio CD / MP3 player / Audio system","Inside speakers","Flat screen TV"],"tenders":["Brig 3.80m - 50HP"]},"crew":[{"name":"Stavros Btalas","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::7704b0a0-246c-11f1-86d3-d79810bbb287/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Stavros, born and raised in mainland Greece in 1983, developed an early affinity for the sea, inspired by the rich maritime heritage of his homeland. Over the past two decades, he has built an extensive career in yachting, gaining valuable experience and earning the respect of both guests and crew.\nStarting his journey as a deckhand, Stavros quickly embraced the demands of life at sea. His dedication, strong work ethic, and natural leadership skills supported his steady progression through the ranks to Captain.\nCaptain Stavros is known for creating a positive and professional atmosphere on board, fostering teamwork and a strong sense of camaraderie among his crew. He leads by example and ensures that every guest enjoys a safe, seamless, and memorable experience.\nWith excellent navigational skills and a deep understanding of weather patterns and local waters, he confidently plans each itinerary with precision and care. Passionate about hospitality, Captain Stavros takes pride in delivering exceptional yachting experiences and unforgettable moments at sea."},{"name":"Claudia Gheorghiu","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::9d4a9ca0-2ced-11f1-b0fe-bf990c334dc6/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Claudia is a dedicated hospitality professional with a strong background in luxury service and guest care. With experience in high-end environments in Mykonos, she has developed a keen eye for detail and a passion for creating personalized guest experiences. Her career spans roles in Greece and Dubai, where she worked in dynamic, fast-paced settings, building excellent organizational and communication skills. She is confident in managing guest requests, coordinating seamless day-to-day service, and ensuring a welcoming and comfortable atmosphere on board. Adaptable and team-oriented, Claudia thrives in a yachting environment, where no two days are the same. Her warm personality, positive attitude, and natural sense of hospitality allow her to anticipate guests’ needs and deliver service with ease and professionalism.\nFluent in Greek, English, and French, and a native Romanian speaker, she communicates effortlessly with international guests. Reliable and detail-focused, Claudia is committed to providing a smooth, enjoyable, and memorable experience for everyone on board."},{"name":"Konstantinos Mitsos","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::19057481779::vessel::3ac5e4d0-3a14-11f0-b5b2-a7af4b30def6::assets::ceeccf50-246c-11f1-86d3-d79810bbb287/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Konstantinos began his professional journey on large commercial vessels, serving as a Deck Cadet. \nDuring this time, he gained valuable hands-on experience in demanding environments, developing strong discipline, a solid work ethic, and a safety-focused approach. Working alongside international crews, he learned the importance of teamwork, adaptability, and effective communication.\nCurrently completing his studies at the Merchant Marine Academy of Epirus, he continues to build his skills and expand his experience at sea. With a positive attitude, great energy, and a strong sense of responsibility, Konstantinos is always willing to assist and support both crew and guests, making him a reliable and approachable member of the team.\nMotivated and detail-oriented, he is committed to maintaining high standards on board and contributing to the smooth operation of the vessel, ensuring a safe and enjoyable experience for everyone on boar"}],"pricing":{"dayPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":390000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":390000,"unit":"DAY"},"dayPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":430000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":430000,"unit":"DAY"},"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":658000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":658000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":2310000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2310000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season (April - May - September - October): Full Day Charter","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-07-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-08-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":430000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"DAY","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":430000,"amount":430000,"conditions":"Includes VAT"}],"total":430000,"subTotal":430000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Greece","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Europe","Southern Europe","Greece"],"coordinates":[24.261736188816826,38.42232351533858],"bbox":[19.646484375,34.934472656249994,28.231835937500023,41.743798828124994]}],"exclusionZones":[],"petsAllowed":false},{"name":"High Season (June - July - August): Full Day Charter ","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-06-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-09-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":390000,"inputAmountTaxed":"IN